		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can implement support for software pixel doubling filters such as Scale2x and hq2x, and then put in a software nearest-neighbor pixel doubler at the same time. VisualBoyAdvance uses this technique.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
